node.text:
Summer is here and I can’t wait to enjoy
all the magical moments it has to offer, like making my original S’mores Sundaes with Palmer! #ad  We took them to the next level with @keebler Fudge Stripes...and lots and lots of sprinkles...yum! 🍪🍦I’ve teamed up with Keebler to make your summer  #smoremagical too. Comment below for a chance to win a S’more Magical prize  pack to enjoy s’mores all summer long! I’ll pick 5 lucky winners on 6/18!  Link in bio for official rules. #nationalfudgeday
